Aaron Shearer: A Life With The Guitar December 29, 2013
By Michael R. Lawrence
Available from mlfilms.com for $29.99

An hour documentary celebrating the life and work
of Aaron Shearer the most influential classic guitar
author and teacher of the 20th Century."
